h1 Listing Status Updates
/This is the button to the form on a new page. We want to get rid of the extra click
/= link_to 'New Status Update', new_students_status_update_path, class: 'btn btn-default'
/That is why we want to render the form here:
= render 'xform'

table.table.table-striped.table-bordered.table-condensed
  thead
    tr
      th Date
      th Title
      th Text
      th
      th
      th

  tbody
    - @status_updates.each do |status_update|
      tr
        td = l status_update.created_at
        td = status_update.title
        td = render_markdown(status_update.content).html_safe
        td = link_to 'Show', students_status_update_path(status_update)
        td = link_to 'Edit', edit_students_status_update_path(status_update)
        td = link_to 'Destroy', students_status_update_path(status_update), data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?'}, method: :delete


